data.description: PRICED TO SELL! This unit offers one of the larger floorplans with two roomy bedrooms and one bath. Eachhome comes will full appliances, including washer/dryer. Secure and safe, you can beat the traffic, leave your car in the underground garage, and pick your pleasure:shopping, dining, movie watching or just strolling the community. Perkins Rowe offers Baton Rouge's only suburban urban living community ... one for all ages andone you will never want to leave. Come check out the view and see what you think!
